(211, 1, '2019-02-21 10:31:00', '2019-02-21 10:31:00', '“Vietnam Expo - Connecting, sharing, and succeeding” is the message that Vietnam Expo International Trade Fair has built and brought.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDeputy Minister of Industry and Trade Tran Quoc Khanh at Vietnam Expo 2018\r\n\r\nThe success of Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades. It is also a well-known event because of the diversity of products, quality products - prestigious brand - creativity of Vietnam that introduces to international friends.\r\n\r\nVietnam Expo is a key event hosted by the Ministry of Industry and Trade (Trade Promotion Agency), receiving strong support from local ministries, domestic and foreign promotion organizations, and Vinexad company responsible The deployment will take place in 4 days, from April 10-13, 2019 at the International Exhibition Center (ICE) - 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hanoi.\r\n\r\nIn 2018, Vietnam Expo gathered 500 businesses from 23 countries and territories, including 6 international pavilions from the Federal Republic of Russia, Cuba, South Korea, Nepal, China and Vietnam. A special feature of Vietnam Expo is the diversified and unique products that are specially displayed in each area including: International pavilion zone - National Brand Area (Vietnam Value) - Machinery and Equipment Product Zone - Food and beverage area.\r\n\r\n“We have thoroughly prepared for the launch of the latest automatic assembly line at Vietnam Expo, our goal is to meet Japanese and Korean electronic component manufacturing companies in the event. \", Representative of Intech Vietnam Co. share.\r\n\r\nMs. Nguyen Thi Oanh, General Director of Hoang Minh Joint Stock Company said: “This is the second time I joined Vietnam Expo, I assess the quality of the business here is very potential, because the customers\' requirements are very high. For environmentally friendly adhesive tape products, produced entirely by natural rubber, no artificial additives, no toxic chemicals, good adhesion on all material surfaces, easily torn by hand. We confidently affirmed that our products meet the standards to supply for large corporations, because we compete with the quality and originality that not all products have. ”\r\n\r\nIn the same view, Mr. Nguyen Van Ly, Viglacera\'s representative, said: “We realize that after each fair participation, we have a large number of customers, especially international visitors. We are interested in new products with environmental friendly elements such as V-Smart smart hygiene, White-bone Granite tiles, energy-saving glass, baked clay bricks ... Through Vietnam Expo, we look forward to strengthening more relationships with partners to enhance the position of Viglacera brand, promote new product exports to markets in and outside the region ”.\r\n\r\nRussian Federation exhibition area - The guest of the recent Vietnam Expo 2018 is especially attracted by the elite products of Russian industry such as precision engineering, automation, weapons, aircraft manufacturing, high-tech electronics ... High-level meetings and seminars taking place during fair days help to open promising cooperation between the two economies of Vietnam and the Russian Federation. According to statistics from the organizers, there were about 8,000 visitors of Vietnam economic groups, businesses and individuals who participated in trade promotion activities at the Russian Pavilion.\r\n\r\n“In the context of a volatile world economy, the increasing participation of Vietnam in new free trade agreements is opening up great opportunities for domestic and international businesses. Therefore, the message of the fair organizers sent to businesses, domestic and international investors through Vietnam Expo is \'Grasping opportunities, cooperating and developing together\' is very meaningful, that is evaluation of Deputy Minister of Industry and Trade Tran Quoc Khanh at the opening ceremony of Vietnam Expo 2018.\r\n\r\nIt is known that Vietnam Expo 2019 continues to build a diversified - special industry model - connecting trade transactions to help domestic and foreign businesses achieve high efficiency, contributing positively to Vietnam to strengthen integration. regional and international economy.\r\n\r\nVietnam Expo 2019 is expected to have the participation of 550 businesses and welcome about 15.00 domestic and foreign visitors to trade in 4 days, from April 10-13, 2019 at 91 Tran Hung Dao Exhibition Center , Hoan Kiem, Hanoi.', 'VIETNAM EXPO - Capture opportunities, cooperate and grow together', 'The success of Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades. It is also a well-known event because of the diversity of products, quality products - prestigious brand - creativity of Vietnam that introduces to international friends.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vietnam-expo-capture-opportunities-cooperate-and-grow-together', '', '', '2019-02-21 10:31:00', '2019-02-21 10:31:00', '', 0, 'http://vietnamexpo.co/?p=211', 0, 'post', '', 0),
