(218, 1, '2019-02-21 10:51:40', '2019-02-21 10:51:40', '<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vietnam Expo 2019 International Trade Fair will be held from April 10-13 at ICE International Exhibition Center - 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi.</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-155 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://vietnamexpo.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vietnam Expo 2019 International Trade Fair will be held from April 10-13.</span></em></p>\r\n<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mr. Nguyen Khac Luan, General Director of Advertising and Trade Fair Joint Stock Company (Vinexad) said that Vietnam Expo 2019 International Trade Fair will be held from April 10-13 at the National Exhibition Center ICE - 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This is an opportunity for international partners to meet pioneering exporters in various product groups such as plastic, rubber, paper, construction materials, industrial support with the purpose of promoting and promoting. High value Vietnamese brand to develop domestic market.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Due to limited infrastructure, the organizers have selected typical businesses to attend in accordance with the stalls such as international zones - Vietnam national brand area (Vietnam Value) - industrial product zone. - consumer food zone.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Up to this point, the organizers and businesses are actively preparing to bring to Vietnam Expo 2019 the latest products and technologies in the impressive and elaborate investment-designed booths.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mr. Nguyen Khac Luan affirmed that Algeria, India, Cambodia, Canada, Armenia, Federal Republic of Russia, Cuba, Taiwan (China), Korea, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, 